text: Eskil Wedholm (2 March 1891 - 10 December 1959) was a Swedish swimmer. He competed in two events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1891 births Category:1959 deaths Category:Swedish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Sweden Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:People from Eskilstuna Category:Male freestyle swimmers
